text: Christine Psiwa (born 1 April 1992) is a Kenyan volleyball player. She is part of the Kenya women's national volleyball team. She participated in the 2018 FIVB Volleyball World Grand Prix. On club level she played for Kenya Pipeline Company. == References == ==Other websites== * christine-psiwa globalsportsarchive Category:1992 births Category:Kenyan volleyball players
